# 📜 Code of Conduct

## 🤝 Pledge
We commit to making BoxyChat a safe, respectful, and welcoming environment for everyone.

## ✅ Expected Behavior
- Be respectful
- Communicate properly
- Follow instructions from staff
- Work collaboratively

## ❌ Unacceptable Behavior
- Harassment or bullying
- Hate speech
- Spam or disruption
- Impersonation
- Abuse of systems or tools

## 🛠️ Enforcement
Violations may result in warnings, restrictions, or removal from the project.

All decisions are handled by BoxTech Studios.

## 🧾 Agreement
By participating, you agree to follow this Code of Conduct.
